<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        table {
            border-spacing: 0;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        td {
            padding: 16px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 16px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 16px;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 0 0 16px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .button {
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .button a {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td class="header">
                Reset Your Password
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="content">
                <h1>Hi there,</h1>
                <p>You recently requested to reset your password. Click the button below to set a new password:</p>
                <div class="button">
                    <a href="<%=base_url%>/reset-password/?token=<%=token%>" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
                </div>
                <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, please ignore this email.</p>
                <p>Thanks,<br>The Azumi Bank Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                &copy; 2024 Azumi Bank. All rights reserved.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
